[[高血壓|高血壓]]是產生人體[[動脈粥樣硬化|動脈粥樣硬化]]、<ref name="pmid19110086">{{cite journal |author=Insull W |title=The pathology of atherosclerosis: plaque development and plaque responses to medical treatment |journal=[[The_American_Journal_of_Medicine|The American Journal of Medicine]] |volume=122 |issue=1 Suppl |pages=S3–S14 |date=January 2009 |pmid=19110086 |doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2008.10.013 }}</ref>[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]、<ref name="pmid19427498">{{cite journal |vauthors=Gaddam KK, Verma A, Thompson M, Amin R, Ventura H |title=Hypertension and cardiac failure in its various forms |journal=[[The_Medical_Clinics_of_North_America|The Medical Clinics of North America]] |volume=93 |issue=3 |pages=665–80 |date=May 2009 |pmid=19427498 |doi=10.1016/j.mcna.2009.02.005 |url=http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0025-7125(09)00020-0 |accessdate=2009-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328134453/http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0025-7125(09)00020-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠狀動脈疾病]]、<ref name="pmid19363848">{{cite journal |author=Agabiti-Rosei E |title=From macro- to microcirculation: benefits in hypertension and diabetes |journal=[[Journal_of_Hypertension|Journal of Hypertension]] |volume= 26|issue= Suppl 3|pages=S15–21 |date=September 2008 |pmid=19363848 |doi=10.1097/01.hjh.0000334602.71005.52 }}</ref><ref name="pmid19427499">{{cite journal |vauthors=Murphy BP, Stanton T, Dunn FG |title=Hypertension and myocardial ischemia |journal=[[The_Medical_Clinics_of_North_America|The Medical Clinics of North America]] |volume=93 |issue=3 |pages=681–95 |date=May 2009 |pmid=19427499 |doi=10.1016/j.mcna.2009.02.003 |url=http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0025-7125(09)00018-2 |accessdate=2009-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328134458/http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0025-7125(09)00018-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[中風|中風]]、<ref name="pmid19393824">{{cite journal |author=White WB |title=Defining the problem of treating the patient with hypertension and arthritis pain |journal=[[The_American_Journal_of_Medicine|The American Journal of Medicine]] |volume=122 |issue=5 Suppl |pages=S3–9 |date=May 2009 |pmid=19393824 |doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2009.03.002 }}</ref>[[腎病變|腎病變]]、<ref name="pmid19195963">{{cite journal |vauthors=Truong LD, Shen SS, Park MH, Krishnan B |title=Diagnosing nonneoplastic lesions in nephrectomy specimens |journal=[[Archives_of_Pathology_&_Laboratory_Medicine|Archives of Pathology & Laboratory Medicine]] |volume=133 |issue=2 |pages=189–200 |date=February 2009 |pmid=19195963 |doi= 10.1043/1543-2165-133.2.189|url=https://www.archivesofpathology.org/doi/10.1043/1543-2165-133.2.189|accessdate=2009-06-20|doi-broken-date=2020-08-23 }}</ref><ref name="pmid11842376">{{cite journal |vauthors=Tracy RE, White S |title=A method for quantifying adrenocortical nodular hyperplasia at autopsy: some use of the method in illuminating hypertension and atherosclerosis |journal=[[Annals_of_Diagnostic_Pathology|Annals of Diagnostic Pathology]] |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=20–9 |date=February 2002 |pmid=11842376 |doi= 10.1053/adpa.2002.30606}}</ref>、和[[周邊動脈阻塞|周邊動脈阻塞]]<ref name="pmid18672184">{{cite journal |author=Aronow WS |title=Hypertension and the older diabetic |journal=[[Clinics_in_Geriatric_Medicine|Clinics in Geriatric Medicine]] |volume=24 |issue=3 |pages=489–501, vi–vii |date=August 2008 |pmid=18672184 |doi=10.1016/j.cger.2008.03.001 |url=http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0749-0690(08)00012-8 |accessdate=2009-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328134511/http://journals.elsevierhealth.com/retrieve/pii/S0749-0690(08)00012-8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pmid19008688">{{cite journal |vauthors=Gardner AW, Afaq A |journal=[[Journal_of_Cardiopulmonary_Rehabilitation_and_Prevention|Journal of Cardiopulmonary Rehabilitation and Prevention]] |volume=28 |issue=6 |pages=349–57 |year=2008 |pmid=19008688 |doi=10.1097/HCR.0b013e31818c3b96 |pmc=2743684|title=Management of Lower Extremity Peripheral Arterial Disease }}</ref>的[[危險因子|危險因子]]，並且也是[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]在[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]方面，發病率和死亡率中最主要的危險因子。<ref name="pmid19149532">{{cite journal |vauthors=Novo S, Lunetta M, Evola S, Novo G |title=Role of ARBs in the blood hypertension therapy and prevention of cardiovascular events |journal=[[Current_Drug_Targets|Current Drug Targets]] |volume=10 |issue=1 |pages=20–5 |date=January 2009 |pmid=19149532 |doi=10.2174/138945009787122897 |url=http://www.bentham-direct.org/pages/content.php?CDT/2009/00000010/00000001/0003J.SGM |accessdate=2009-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328134515/http://www.bentham-direct.org/pages/content.php?CDT%2F2009%2F00000010%2F00000001%2F0003J.SGM |archive-date=2020-03-28 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>在1940年之前，年齡在50歲以上的人群中約有23％的死亡歸因於高血壓。嚴重的高血壓須利用手術治療。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Craig WM |title=Surgical Treatment of Hypertension |journal=Br Med J |volume=2 |issue=4120 |pages=1215–9 |year=1939 |pmid=20782854 |pmc=2178707 |doi= 10.1136/bmj.2.4120.1215|url=}}</ref>
 
早期治療高血壓的方式包括使用[[季銨鹽|季銨鹽]][[交感神經|交感神經]]系統阻滯劑，但由於當時尚未確定高血壓對健康產生的長期後果，加上這類化合物有嚴重的副作用，又必須通過注射給藥，而未廣泛使用。
 
1952年，[[汽巴精化|汽巴精化]]的研究人員發現第一種口服[[血管舒張|血管舒張]]劑[[肼屈嗪|肼屈嗪]]
。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Sneader |first1=Walter |title=Drug Discovery. A History |url=https://archive.org/details/drugdiscoveryhis00snea |location=New York |publisher=Wiley |year=2005 |page=[https://archive.org/details/drugdiscoveryhis00snea/page/n384 371] |accessdate=}}</ref>使用肼屈嗪的單一療法的主要缺點是有效性會隨時間下降（{{link-en|快速耐受性|tachyphylaxis}}）。1950年代中期，默克藥廠的Karl H. Beyer、James M. Sprague、John E. Baer、和Frederick C. Novello四位發現並開發出{{link-en|氯噻嗪|chlorothiazide}}，氯噻嗪是當今使用最廣泛的降血壓藥。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Beyer KH |title=Chlorothiazide. How the thiazides evolved as antihypertensive therapy |journal=Hypertension |volume=22 |issue=3 |pages=388–91 |year=1993 |pmid=8349332 |doi= 10.1161/01.hyp.22.3.388|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_hypertension_1993-09_22_3/page/388}}</ref>這種進展與高血壓患者的死亡率大幅下降有關。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=BORHANI NO, HECHTER HH |journal=Public Health Rep |volume=79 |issue= 2|pages=147–60 |year=1964 |pmid=14119789 |pmc=1915335 |doi= 10.2307/4592077|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_public-health-reports_1964-02_79_2/page/147|jstor=4592077 |title=Recent Changes in CVR Disease Mortality in California: An Epidemiologic Appraisal }}</ref>發明人因"挽救無數人的生命，並減輕數以百萬計高血壓患者的痛苦"而獲得1975年[[公共衛生|公共衛生]]的[[拉斯克獎|拉斯克獎]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/formaward.htm |title=The Lasker Foundation - Awards |website= |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223033435/http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/formaward.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
在2009年，國際性醫學非政府組織[[考科藍|考科藍]]發表的評論，結論是[[噻嗪類|噻嗪類]]降血壓藥可降低高血壓患者的死亡風險（[[相對風險|相對風險]] 0.89）、中風（相對風險 0.63）、心臟病（相對風險 0.84）、和心血管狀況（相對風險 0.70）。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Wright|first1=James M.|last2=Musini|first2=Vijaya M.|last3=Gill|first3=Rupam|date=2018-04-18|title=First-line drugs for hypertension|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|volume=4|pages=CD001841|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001841.pub3|issn=1469-493X|pmc=6513559|pmid=29667175}}</ref>在隨後的年份中，有其他類別的降血壓藥被開發出，並在組合療法中受到廣泛使用，包括環利尿劑（ [[呋塞米|呋塞米]]，商品名Lasix，德國藥廠Hoechst Pharmaceuticals，1963年）、<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Stason WB, Cannon PJ, Heinemann HO, Laragh JH |title=Furosemide. A clinical evaluation of its diuretic action |journal=Circulation |volume=34 |issue=5 |pages=910–20 |date=November 1966 |pmid=5332332 |doi= 10.1161/01.cir.34.5.910|s2cid=886870 |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_circulation_1966-11_34_5/page/910}}</ref>[[β受體阻滯劑|β受體阻滯劑]]（[[帝國化學工業|帝國化學工業]]，1964年）、<ref name="Black JW, Crowther AF, Shanks RG, Smith LH, Dornhorst AC 1964 1080–1081">{{cite journal|vauthors=Black JW, Crowther AF, Shanks RG, Smith LH, Dornhorst AC |title=A new adrenergic betareceptor antagonist | journal=[[The_Lancet|The Lancet]] |volume=283 |issue=7342 |pages=1080–1081 |year=1964 |pmid=14132613 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(64)91275-9}}</ref>[[血管緊張肽I轉化酶抑制劑|血管緊張肽I轉化酶抑制劑]]（ACE抑制劑）、和[[血管緊張素II受體拮抗劑|血管緊張素II受體拮抗劑]]。 無論患者是否患有高血壓，ACE抑制劑可降低糖尿病患者新發腎病的風險（相對風險 0.71）以及死亡（相對風險 0.84）。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Lv J, Perkovic V, Foote CV, Craig ME, Craig JC, Strippoli GF |title=Antihypertensive agents for preventing diabetic kidney disease |journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |volume=12 |issue= |pages=CD004136 |year=2012 |pmid=23235603 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD004136.pub3 |url=}}</ref>。

====口服避孕藥====
第二次世界大戰之前，許多國家都禁止[[生育控制|生育控制]]，在美國，甚至有關避孕方法的討論有時也會導致依據{{link-en|康斯托克法律|Comstock laws}}而提起訴訟。因此，[[複合口服避孕藥|口服避孕藥]]的發展歷史，與{{link-en|美國節育運動|birth control movement in the United States}}以及其中激進主義者[[山額夫人|山額夫人]]、{{link-en|瑪麗·丹內特|Mary Dennett}}、和[[艾瑪·高德曼|艾瑪·高德曼]]三位等的努力息息相關。基於[[格雷戈里·平卡斯|格雷戈里·平卡斯]]的基礎研究，以及美國藥廠{{link-en|Laboratorios Syntex SA|Syntex}}的[[卡爾·傑拉西|卡爾·傑拉西]]和藥廠{{link-en|G.D. Searle＆Co.|G.D. Searle, LLC}}（現為輝瑞公司旗下的品牌）的{{link-en|Frank Colton|Frank B. Colton}}兩位開發的[[孕酮|孕酮]]合成方法，G.D. Searle＆Co.開發出世界第一種口服避孕藥-{{link-en|異炔諾酮|Mestranol/noretynodrel}}（商品名Enovid），這藥物在1960年獲得FDA批准。最初的配方中含有過量的激素，會引起嚴重的副作用。但是到1962年，已有120萬名美國婦女服用過此藥，到1965年，數字已增至650萬。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/wnet/need-to-know/health/a-brief-history-of-the-birth-control-pill/480/ |title=A brief history of the birth control pill - The pill timeline | Need to Know | PBS |format= |website= |accessdate= |date=2010-05-07 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230732/https://www.pbs.org/wnet/need-to-know/health/a-brief-history-of-the-birth-control-pill/480/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/why-the-oral-contraceptive-is-just-known-as-the-pill-4337831/?no-ist |title=Why the Oral Contraceptive Is Just Known as "The Pill" |format= |publisher=smithsonianmag.com |accessdate= |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109222039/https://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/why-the-oral-contraceptive-is-just-known-as-the-pill-4337831/?no-ist |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/250337.stm |title=BBC News | HEALTH | A short history of the pill |format= |website= |accessdate= |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113085204/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/250337.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fda.gov/AboutFDA/WhatWeDo/History/ProductRegulation/SelectionsFromFDLIUpdateSeriesonFDAHistory/ucm092009.htm |title=FDA's Approval of the First Oral Contraceptive, Enovid |website= |accessdate= |archive-date=2017-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723090206/https://www.fda.gov/AboutFDA/WhatWeDo/History/ProductRegulation/SelectionsFromFDLIUpdateSeriesonFDAHistory/ucm092009.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>便利形式的臨時避孕藥的出現，導致美國社會習俗發生巨大變化，包括婦女擴大的生活方式選擇，減少婦女依賴男性做的避孕措施，女性晚婚、婚前同居因此增加。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-15984258 |title=BBC News - How the contraceptive pill changed Britain |format= |work=BBC News |accessdate= |date=2011-12-04 |last1=Cafe |first1=Rebecca |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616094742/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-15984258 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====沙利度胺和基福弗-哈里斯修正案====
在美國，[[田納西州|田納西州]]參議員{{link-en|基福弗|Carey Estes Kefauver}}於1959年主持的國會聽證會中推動對《聯邦食品、藥品和化妝品法案》的修訂。這項聽證會涉及廣泛的政策議題，包括廣告濫用、引起疑慮的藥物療效、以及產業需要更多的監管。雖然改革動力在長時間的辯論中暫時受到阻撓，但由於當時一項事件，突顯全面監管更有需要，為新法律的通過提供助力。
