2月26日，[[美國衛生與公共服務部|美國衛生與公共服務部]]部長（前藥廠首席執行官）[[亞歷克斯·阿扎|亞歷克斯·阿扎]]在眾議院{{link-en|能源和商業委員會|House Energy and Commerce Committee}}上作證。阿扎在會議上一再拒絕說所有美國人都可受到[[2019冠狀病毒|2019冠狀病毒]]疫苗接種或治療，而不僅是有經濟能力者才能享有，詢問的議員批評他的立場。幾個小時後，據說對這位部長的處理能力持懷疑態度的川普總統突然將處理這次瘟疫的責任轉移給副總統邁克·彭斯。總統隨後對新聞界解釋，阿扎仍將繼續擔任衛生和公共服務部部長；報導說，川普總統在危機期間為保住顏面而未將他解職。<ref name=rich>{{cite web |last1=Johnson |first1=Jake |title='An Outrage': HHS Chief Azar Refuses to Vow Coronavirus Vaccine Will Be Affordable for All, Not Just the Rich |url=https://www.commondreams.org/news/2020/02/27/outrage-hhs-chief-azar-refuses-vow-coronavirus-vaccine-will-be-affordable-all-not |website=Common Dreams |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130022538/https://www.commondreams.org/news/2020/02/27/outrage-hhs-chief-azar-refuses-vow-coronavirus-vaccine-will-be-affordable-all-not |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=pence>{{cite web |last1=Olorunnipa |first1=Toluse |last2=Dawsey |first2=Josh |last3=Abutaleb |first3=Yasmeen |title=Trump downplays risk, places Pence in charge of coronavirus outbreak response |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-downplays-risk-places-pence-in-charge-of-coronavirus-outbreak-response/2020/02/26/ab246e94-58b1-11ea-9000-f3cffee23036_story.html |website=Washington Post |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2020-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214113658/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-downplays-risk-places-pence-in-charge-of-coronavirus-outbreak-response/2020/02/26/ab246e94-58b1-11ea-9000-f3cffee23036_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
